title: NFL Week 14 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 14 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap every Sunday game on the Week 14 NFL schedule. Highlights include the Seahawks vs. Eagles matchup, Colts vs. Browns and Brady vs. Rivers on Sunday Night Football.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
